Package: pathr
Title: Work with URL and file paths
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kyle", "Harris", , "koderkow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of pathr is to simplify the process of string manipulations for URLs and file paths. This uses modified functions from the {httr} to create opinionated functions that allow working with URLs and paths easier.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
